Text: Detroit Cold RollBelow are the LDC points for Detroit Cold Roll I hope this helps If not please let me know and Ill forward back to Tony Thanks for your help again Ken Forwarded by Ken SissinghCorpEnron on AM Tony Wilson on AM To Ken Sissingh cc Subject Dear Ken I spoke to Michcon regarding their gas city gates They have over connection points in the state The nearest ones to Gibraltar although they will transport it from anywhere because the gas loses its identity when it is mixed with other gas already in the pipes are Panhandle River Rouge ANRWillow Run Great Lakes TransmissionBelle River I am still arranging to get the Pickling invoices How many months do you need Regards Tony Wilson
